org.springframework.data.redis.core.index

注释类型 Indexed


  • @Documented
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value={FIELD,ANNOTATION_TYPE})
public @interface Indexed
    Mark properties value to be included in a secondary index.
    Uses Redis SET for storage.
    The value will be part of the key built for the index.
    从以下版本开始:
    1.7
